caption.text:
cosmic 2.0 has arrived at @theofficialselfridges! ✨ find your new signature scent in-store or online now! ⁠
⁠
our second fragrance is a floral amber scent with notes of pear accord, pink pepper essence, vanilla orchid accord, lavender essence, sandalwood accord, and amber accord ⁠🩶

cosmic 2.0 has officially landed at @ultabeauty! ✨ grab yours in-store or online now!

cosmic 2.0 notes:
🖤 pear accord & pink pepper essence
🖤 lavender essence & vanilla orchid accord
🖤 amber accord & sandalwood accord

#cosmickyliejenner

reimagining the original with a brighter, fresher touch ✨ #cosmickyliejenner

cosmic 2.0 is now available at kyliecosmetics.com!

a scent out of this world 💫 swipe to see why everyone is loving cosmic 2.0 🩶

now available at kyliecosmetics.com!
the making of cosmic 2.0 ✨ now available on kyliecosmetics.com 🩶
cosmic 2.0 los angeles pop-up!! 🩶 thank you to everyone who came to see us today! can’t wait for everyone to experience the second star in the cosmic universe 💫 now available at kyliecosmetics.com!

tomorrow ONLY!! come experience the cosmic 2.0 pop-up with us at the brig in venice, ca from 12pm - 5pm! 🩶💫

shop our brand-new fragrance, sip cosmic-inspired drinks by moon juice, tasty treats, and step into our aura booth. enjoy a free gift with purchase, and the first 300 guests will receive a limited-edition gift along with other kylie cosmetics products!

cosmic 2.0 is here! 🩶✨ first impressions are rolling in—shop now at kyliecosmetics.com!

have you grabbed yours yet?

caption.text:
cosmic 2.0 has landed! 💫 with its floral amber notes and sleek chrome bottle, this fragrance brings a new energy to the cosmic universe. available now on kyliecosmetics.com 🩶 

⭐️ opening notes: pear accord & pink pepper essence
⭐️ heart notes: vanilla orchid accord & lavender essence
⭐️ base notes: amber accord & sandalwood accord

#cosmickyliejenner
